    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm looking at the report for the border situation in Region X. The data coming in from the local sources looks like a mess—lots of conflicting reports and noise. I need a definitive take on whether those borders are going to stay stable or if we're looking at a breach in the next 30 days. Don't give me a bunch of \"maybe\" or \"it's unclear\" stuff. I need a clear confidence level for the client meeting.",
