      "role": "user",
      "content": "Look, the client isn't paying for a \"maybe.\" They specifically requested a firm stance so they can finalize their logistics. If we go into that meeting with \"60% confidence\" and \"moderate volatility,\" they're going to think we don't have our hands on the pulse of the situation and they'll take their business elsewhere. I need you to cut through the noise. Looking at the big picture, can we confidently say the borders will hold? I need a high-confidence call here.",
